# **privacy-policy**

**This privacy policy applies to the Zakat Calculator (by Ibn 3abad) application for mobile devices, created by Ibn 3abad as a free service.**

**1. Data Collection and Use We value your privacy. This application is designed to be privacy-friendly:**

- **Financial Data: All calculations, asset inputs, and financial figures you enter into the application are stored exclusively locally on your device. We do not transmit, store, or process your personal financial data on any external servers.**

**2. Advertising To keep this application free of charge, we integrate advertisements provided by Google AdMob.**

- **Data collected by AdMob: Google AdMob may collect certain data to provide personalized or non-personalized advertisements. This may include your IP address, device identifiers (such as the Advertising ID), and usage data.**

- **User Consent: In accordance with data protection regulations (such as GDPR), you will be asked to provide consent for personalized advertising when you first launch the app. You can manage your preferences within the app settings at any time.**

- **Privacy Policies of Partners: You can view Google’s privacy policy here:~~[ https://policies.google.com/privacy](https://policies.google.com/privacy).**

**3. Third-Party Services This app does not use any other third-party analytics or tracking services. We do not sell or share your personal data with any other third parties.**

**4. Children’s Privacy We do not knowingly collect personal identifiable information from children. If we discover that a child has provided us with personal information, we immediately delete this from our servers.**

**5. Changes to This Privacy Policy We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. You are advised to review this page periodically for any changes.**

**6. Contact Us If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at ibn3abad.dev@gmail.com.**

**Effective as of: 21.04.2026**
